                     <interp inst="t18360104-323-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18360104-cd-15" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360104-323-offence-1 t18360104-cd-15"></join>19th of De<lb></lb>cember</rs>, 6lbs. of ham, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360104-name-155" type="victimName">
